MOTING THE USE OF FEDERAL DOCUMENTS' AN EXPERIMENTAL CURRENT AWARENESSSERVICE.     DISCUSSES THE EFFECTIVENESS OF AN EXPERIMENTAL CURRENT AWARENESS SERVICE FORPROMOTING THE USE OF FEDERAL DOCUMENTS. BASED ON THE RESULTS FROM AQUESTIONNAIRE, THE USE PATTERNS OF FACULTIES IN ECONOMICS AND POLITICALSCIENCE ARE EXAMINED. THE STUDY ANALYSES THE CURRENT AWARENESS SERVICE AS AMEANS FOR IDENTIFYING DOCUMENTS AND THE IMPACT OF THE SERVICE ON THE FACULTY.AMONG THE USERS OF DOCUMENTS, THE SERVICE WAS AN AID TO RESEARCH, ANDINCREASED THEIR AWARENESS OF THE ABUNDANCE AND SCOPE OF DOCUMENTS, AS WELL ASINCREASING THEIR USE OF DOCUMENTS. (A COPY OF THE QUESTIONNAIRE IS AVAILABLEFROM THE AUTHOR UPON REQUEST)